# Google Cloud OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application type).
# Create one at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# - Enable the "Google Drive API" and "Google Sheets API" on the project.
# - Add your dev/prod origin(s) (e.g. http://localhost:5173) to "Authorized JavaScript origins".
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the value.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
